/>\n* {{Flag|Thailand}}: Member of the [[List of orders and medals of Thailand#Royal medals|Royal Decoration King Bhumibol Adulyadej]]<ref>{{cite web |url = https://www.pinterest.com/pin/467178161318102862/ |title = Princess Sirindhorn... - THailand : Royal Family - Pinterest - Princesses and Thailand |work = Pinterest|accessdate = February 23, 2016}}</ref><ref>\n[https://s-media-cache-ak0.pinimg.com/736x/67/5e/97/675e9749dfebb04260afbdae30860d4f.jpg wearing badge formed medal under the star of the order of the 9 gems]</ref><ref>{{cite web |url = https://www.pinterest.com/pin/525443481498988659/ |title = Her Royal Highness Princess Maha Chakri Sirindhorn - Thai Monarchy: King Bhumibol Adulyadej - Pinterest - Royals and Princesses |work = Pinterest|accessdate = February 23, 2016}}</ref>\n* {{Flag|Thailand}}: Member of the [[List of orders and medals of Thailand#Royal medals|Royal Decoration King Vajiralongkorn]]\n* {{Flag|Thailand}}: Recipient of the [[List of orders and medals of Thailand#Royal medals|King Bhumibol Adulyadej Rajaruchi Royal Medal]]\n* {{Flag|Thailand}}: Recipient of the [[List of orders and medals of Thailand#Royal medals|Freemen Safeguarding Medal, First Class]]<ref name=\"Medals\">Zen Journalist, [http://www.zenjournalist.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/zany.jpg wearing her Medals]</ref>\n* {{Flag|Thailand}}: Recipient of the [[List of orders and medals of Thailand#Royal medals|Dushdi Mala Medal]]<ref name=\"Medals\" /><ref name=\"Badges2\">Wiki Commons, [https://commons.m.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Princess_Sirindhorn_2009-12-7_Royal_Thai_Government_House_4.jpg wearing some Medals]</ref>\n* {{Flag|Thailand}}: Recipient of the [[List of orders and medals of Thailand#Royal medals|Border Service Medal]]<ref name=\"Medals\" />\n* {{Flag|Thailand}}: Recipient of the [[List of orders and medals of Thailand#Royal medals|Chakra Mala Medal]]<ref name=\"Medals\" />\n* {{Flag|Thailand}}: Recipient of the [[Order of Ramkeerati|Boy Scout Citation Medal, First Class]]<ref name=\"Medals\" />\n* {{Flag|Thailand}}: Recipient of the [[List of orders and medals of Thailand#Royal medals|Red Cross Medal of Appreciation, First Class]]<ref name=\"Medals\" />\n* {{Flag|Thailand}}: Recipient of the [[List of orders and medals of Thailand#Royal medals|King Bhumibol Adulyadej Silver Jubilee Medal]]<ref name=\"Medals\" />\n* {{Flag|Thailand}}: Recipient of the [[List of orders and medals of Thailand#Royal medals|Crown Prince Maha Vajiralongkorn Investiture Medal]]\n* {{Flag|Thailand}}: Recipient of the [[List of orders and medals of Thailand#Royal medals|Bicentennial Medal of the Rattanakosin Kingdom]]\n* {{Flag|Thailand}}: Recipient of the [[List of orders and medals of Thailand#Royal medals|50th Birthday Medal of Queen Sirikit]]\n* {{Flag|Thailand}}: Recipient of the [[List of orders and medals of Thailand#Royal medals|84th Birthday Medal of Princess Mother Srinagarindra]]\n* {{Flag|Thailand}}: Recipient of the [[List of orders and medals of Thailand#Royal medals|60th Birthday Medal of King Bhumibol Adulyadej]]\n* {{Flag|Thailand}}: Recipient of the [[List of orders and medals of Thailand#Royal medals|Longest Reign Commemorative Medal]]\n* {{Flag|Thailand}}: Recipient of the [[List of orders and medals of Thailand#Royal medals|60th Birthday Medal of Queen Sirikit]]\n* {{Flag|Thailand}}: Recipient of the [[List of orders and medals of Thailand#Royal medals|King Bhumibol Adulyadej Golden Jubilee Medal]]\n* {{Flag|Thailand}}: Recipient of the [[List of orders and medals of Thailand#Royal medals|6th Cycle Birthday Medal of King Bhumibol Adulyadej]]<ref name=\"Badges2\" />\n* {{Flag|Thailand}}: Recipient of the [[List of orders and medals of Thailand#Royal medals|72nd Birthday Medal of Queen Sirikit]]\n* {{Flag|Thailand}}: Recipient of the [[List of orders and medals of Thailand#Royal medals|King Bhumibol Adulyadej Diamond Jubilee Medal]]<ref name=\"Badges\" />\n* {{Flag|Thailand}}: Recipient of the [[List of orders and medals of Thailand#Royal medals|7th Cycle Birthday Medal of King Bhumibol Adulyadej]]<ref name=\"Badges\" />\n* {{Flag|Thailand}}: Recipient of the [[List of orders and medals of Thailand#Royal medals|60th Birthday Medal of Crown Prince Maha Vajiralongkorn]]\n* {{Flag|Thailand}}: Recipient of the [[List of orders and medals of Thailand#Medals for Conmemorative Occasion|Commemorative Medal on the Occasion of the Coronation of H.M. King Rama X]]\n\n====Foreign honours====\n* {{Flag|Austria}}: Grand Cross of the [[Decoration of Honour for Services to the Republic of Austria|Order of Honour for Services to the Republic of Austria]] ({{lang-th|\u0e40\u0e04\u0e23\u0e37\u0e48\u0e2d\u0e07\u0e2d\u0e34\u0e2a\u0e23\u0e34\u0e22\u0e32\u0e20\u0e23\u0e13\u0e4c\u0e01\u0e34\u0e15\u0e34\u0e04\u0e38\u0e13\u0e41\u0e2b\u0e48\u0e07\u0e2a\u0e32\u0e18\u0e32\u0e23\u0e13\u0e23\u0e31\u0e10\u0e2d\u0e2d\u0e2a\u0e40\u0e15\u0e23\u0e35\u0e22}})<ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.parlament.gv.at/PAKT/VHG/XXIV/AB/AB_10542/imfname_251156.pdf |title = Reply to a parliamentary question about the Decoration of Honour|language=German |page = 1124|accessdate = 20 September 2014}}</ref>\n* {{Flag|Brunei}}: Knight Grand Cross of the [[List of post-nominal letters (Brunei)|Most Esteemed Family Order of Brunei]]\n* {{Flag|China}}: Recipient of the [[Medal of Friendship]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/english/2019-09/17/c_138399163.htm|title=China Focus: 42 individuals awarded national medals, honorary titles - Xinhua {{!}} English.news.cn|website=www.xinhuanet.com|access-date=2019-09-29}}</ref>\n* {{Flag|Denmark}}: Knight Grand Cross of the [[Order of the Dannebrog]]\n* {{Flag|France}}: Commander of [[Ordre des Palmes Academiques|Order of Academic Palms, 1st Class]]\n* {{Flag|Germany}}: Grand Cross 1st Class of the [[Order of Merit of the Federal Republic of Germany]]\n* {{Flag|India}}: [[Padma Bhushan]]<ref>http://pib.nic.in/newsite/PrintRelease.aspx?relid=157675</ref>\n* {{Flag|Japan}}: Paulownia Dame Grand Cordon o