cipient of the [[List of orders and medals of Thailand#Royal medals|72nd Birthday Medal of Queen Sirikit]]\n* {{Flag|Thailand}}: Recipient of the [[List of orders and medals of Thailand#Royal medals|King Bhumibol Adulyadej Diamond Jubilee Medal]]<ref name=\"Badges\" />\n* {{Flag|Thailand}}: Recipient of the [[List of orders and medals of Thailand#Royal medals|7th Cycle Birthday Medal of King Bhumibol Adulyadej]]<ref name=\"Badges\" />\n* {{Flag|Thailand}}: Recipient of the [[List of orders and medals of Thailand#Royal medals|60th Birthday Medal of Crown Prince Maha Vajiralongkorn]]\n* {{Flag|Thailand}}: Recipient of the [[List of orders and medals of Thailand#Medals for Conmemorative Occasion|Commemorative Medal on the Occasion of the Coronation of H.M. King Rama X]]\n\n====Foreign honours====\n* {{Flag|Austria}}: Grand Cross of the [[Decoration of Honour for Services to the Republic of Austria|Order of Honour for Services to the Republic of Austria]] ({{lang-th|\u0e40\u0e04\u0e23\u0e37\u0e48\u0e2d\u0e07\u0e2d\u0e34\u0e2a\u0e23\u0e34\u0e22\u0e32\u0e20\u0e23\u0e13\u0e4c\u0e01\u0e34\u0e15\u0e34\u0e04\u0e38\u0e13\u0e41\u0e2b\u0e48\u0e07\u0e2a\u0e32\u0e18\u0e32\u0e23\u0e13\u0e23\u0e31\u0e10\u0e2d\u0e2d\u0e2a\u0e40\u0e15\u0e23\u0e35\u0e22}})<ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.parlament.gv.at/PAKT/VHG/XXIV/AB/AB_10542/imfname_251156.pdf |title = Reply to a parliamentary question about the Decoration of Honour|language=German |page = 1124|accessdate = 20 September 2014}}</ref>\n* {{Flag|Brunei}}: Knight Grand Cross of the [[List of post-nominal letters (Brunei)|Most Esteemed Family Order of Brunei]]\n* {{Flag|China}}: Recipient of the [[Medal of Friendship]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/english/2019-09/17/c_138399163.htm|title=China Focus: 42 individuals awarded national medals, honorary titles - Xinhua {{!}} English.news.cn|website=www.xinhuanet.com|access-date=2019-09-29}}</ref>\n* {{Flag|Denmark}}: Knight Grand Cross of the [[Order of the Dannebrog]]\n* {{F